So Mr. Specker suggested a way to approximate better a parabola and I find the suggestion good, but still not a final solution. In any case, I strongly suggest that Abaqus creates a feature in sketcher to be able to create parabolas. Parabolas have very unique physical properties and it is a pity useful in many fields that you can not create them directly in the
